from pyecharts import Pie
experience_count = data.groupby('类型')['平均工资'].count()#平均工资
print(experience_count.reset_index()['类型'].tolist())
print(experience_count.reset_index()['平均工资'].tolist())
attr = experience_count.reset_index()['类型'].tolist()
value = experience_count.reset_index()['平均工资'].tolist()

# 初始化图表通用属性
pie = Pie(title = "工作类型要求占比",
          title_pos = 'center', # 标题居中
          title_top = 'bottom', # 标题在底部
          title_color = '#0000ff', # 标题颜色设置为蓝色，256位rgb格式
          background_color = "#aee", # 设置背景颜色，16位rgb格式
          width = 600,height = 420)

pie.add("", attr, value, is_label_show=True)
pie
